             was indicted for <rs id="t18121028-95-off543" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18121028-95-off543" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18121028-95-off543" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18121028-95-cd544" type="crimeDate">29th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121028-95-off543 t18121028-95-cd544"></join>, a sack, value 2 s. and four bushels of wheat, value 35 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18121028-95-victim1005" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Jordan
                  <interp inst="t18121028-95-victim1005" type="surname" value="Jordan"></interp>
